---
title: Sloppy Joe Style Loaded Fries with cabbage slaw and pickled chilli
description: A sloppy Joe is the name given to a burger made with mince meat that hasn't been formed into a patty. The dish hails from the USA—Sioux City, Iowa to be exact! This dish is a (further) deconstructed version which tops crispy fries and also features chipotle paste and spicy pickled peppers.
